# ─── ACLED Conflict Data (OPTIONAL but RECOMMENDED) ──────────────────────────
# Register free at: https://acleddata.com/register/
# ACLED provides detailed conflict event data (fatalities, actors, event types).
# Without these credentials, ACLED data is skipped and the app relies on GDELT only.

# Primary auth method: OAuth (email + password)
ACLED_EMAIL=your_email@example.com
ACLED_PASSWORD=your_password_here

# Fallback auth method: Legacy API key (used if OAuth token fails)
ACLED_API_KEY=your_api_key_here

# ─── Notes ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# All other data sources (GDELT, RSS feeds, FlightRadar24, AIS, Tzeva Adom)
# are public APIs and require NO authentication.
#
# No database is required. All data is fetched on-demand and cached in memory.
